This article is a letter of support sent to Senators from law clerks of Judge Sonia Sotomayor. The letter expresses their full support for her nomination to the Supreme Court. The law clerks highlight Judge Sotomayor's qualifications, including her extensive federal judicial experience and her commitment to the rule of law. They also praise her intellectual prowess, work ethic, and practical judgment. The law clerks emphasize Judge Sotomayor's inspiring life story and her dedication to understanding the concerns of individuals from all walks of life. They conclude by urging the Senators to confirm her as the next Associate Justice of the Supreme Court.